metadata.name: Mosaic of Memes Mint Pass
metadata.description:
Project to let Memes make the Memes, take over web3 and help create an open metaverse. Mosaics of Memes by 6529 (not by 6529).

This mosaic of the first meme card was created using all the individual memes from Season 1 of The Memes by 6529.

This genesis NFT will serve as a mint/burn pass for all future mosaics from Season 1.  All burns will be a free and simple 1 to 1. No excessive "burnzinomics" here.  There will also be free claims and rewards for people who hold onto at least 1 genesis pass.
